ies. I'm verifying the data aligns with the front-end components within `app/portal/analytics/page.tsx` that render these counts, especially `WorkspaceCard`. I need to ensure a correct and useful data structure.\n\n\n**Confirming Data Integrity**\n\nI've just validated the case sensitivity of the project status within the mock data. The code uses lowercase `\"active\"`, so there are no data misalignment issues. I confirmed it in `lib/api-auth.ts`, ensuring the data is correctly rendered for projects. This resolves my concerns.\n\n\n"}}
